Yes....like it says in this song...
I am coward who became a poet for her love.
I wrote every poem in his name, describe his presence...with the best words i could ever think of.

What should i do now?
I dont have any words that can lead my earnest plee to him.
How could my lame poem reach to him,
When my dear god closed his ears to my prayer
So,why would my love  listen to the poem with words that's nothing new...
